name: What Could Go Wrong
description:
STORY

One day without warning, your family's fortune was lost overnight.
In a time where top influencers earn huge money on social media, you decide to begin your journey as a new influencer.
Get to meet and collab with amazing top influencers who seem to really like you too! What could go wrong…?

Developed by

Adele Sim – Art

Bryan Low – Dialogue Writer

Grace Chua – Programming, Dialogue Editor, Music
